urgency_threshold_miss.description: Aggregate score fell on wrong side of level threshold boundary

category_priority_conflict.description: Multiple categories present, wrong one ranked higher by keyword count

name_null_extraction.description: Name not extracted at all when present in transcript

amount_null_extraction.description: Amount extracted as null when transcript contains a stated amount

name_intro_pattern_missing.description: Common introduction pattern not matched by any regex

category_vocabulary_gap.description: Expected category not in engine NEEDS_KEYWORDS list

name_partial_capture.description: First name captured but last name dropped, or vice versa

category_multi_signal_conflict.description: Contextual signals for multiple categories are nearly equal

amount_partial_match_override.description: Partial spoken number matched instead of full compound form

amount_spoken_number_failure.description: Spoken number form not in SPOKEN_NUMBERS map

amount_tolerance_exceeded.description: Amount detected but outside tolerance threshold

amount_false_positive.description: Amount extracted when none was expected (wage/age/date confusion)

urgency_multiplier_override.description: Category bonus multiplier pushed score to wrong level
